These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
City: berlin, miami, marseilles, prague
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, climbing, tennis
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, goat, turtle
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, bus, ship
 1. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
10. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
11. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to prague##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| City          | prague     | miami   | berlin | marseilles |
| Sport   | swimming | biathlon    | tennis   | climbing    |
| Pet           | goat       | turtle   | cat   | bird     |
| Transport     | bike       | airplane | ship  | bus      |

