.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, tennis, cricket, rugby
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, mystery
There 4 different types of food: mango, pineapple, pumpkin, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
 3. the person eating zucchini is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 8. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person eating pineapple is the person watching mystery movies##1
10. the person eating zucchini is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Sport      | tennis       | weightlifting | rugby     | cricket     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | crime       | mystery | martial-arts |
| Food           | pumpkin       | zucchini    | pineapple     | mango         |
| Transport     | skateboard | scooter     | car     | roller       |

