 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
 5. the futuristic house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 8. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 9. the person traveling to london is in an even position##4
10. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person traveling to london##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
