 3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
 4. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
 5. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 6. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person traveling to hannover is between the fan of metal and the person traveling to london##2
 8. the musician is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
11. the fan of pop is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
12. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the firefighter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
