There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, indonesian, nigerian
 1. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person eating plum##2
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
 3. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 5. the person eating plum is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 8. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
12. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
13. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
