 7. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 8. the thai is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the australian is the person eating cabbage##1
10. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
11. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing domino##5
12. the person eating cabbage is in an even position##4

