There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, amber, mauve, white
There 4 different types of food: banana, lime, potato, radish
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, roller, airplane, scooter
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
 2. the person eating banana is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is between the person who likes lilac and the person driving the scooter##2
 4. the person eating lime is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
 5. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 6. the person who likes white is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 8. the person eating banana is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
 9. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5
12. the person eating lime is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Color      | white   | lilac | amber   | mauve          |
| Food          | lime    | radish        | potato     | banana          |
| Transport           | roller | airplane        | taxi | scooter |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

