.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, reading, hiking, gardening
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, doctor, journalist, musician
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, italian, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, snowmobile, taxi
 1. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
 3. the musician is on the left or right of the architect##3
 4. the italian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 5. the doctor is between the journalist and the indonesian##2
 6. the italian is in an odd position##4
 7. the journalist is the colombian##1
 8. the italian is on the left of the colombian##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the italian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby      | hiking   | gardening      | reading | camping     |
| Job           | musician   | architect  | doctor        | journalist |
| Nationality   | german     | indonesian     | italian      | colombian   |
| Transport     | skateboard | snowmobile | taxi          | roller     |

