.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
House: futuristic, ranch-style, cottage, cape-cod
City: venice, boston, hamburg, miami
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, drama, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, gospel, punk, soul
 1. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 2. the fan of soul is the futuristic house##1
 3. the cottage house is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 4. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 6. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to venice##5
 9. the fan of punk is on the right of the futuristic house##1
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the cottage house##5
11. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| House          | futuristic | cottage  | cape-cod    | ranch-style       |
| City           | boston  | miami | hamburg | venice  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | drama   | martial-arts  | action     |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | punk    | gospel        | electronic |

 